{"tid":227550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個腥港蝗族嘅奇人奇事","createTime":"2017-05-03T09:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T15:19:14.000Z","uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24f4d2652b8221cc41ee6d7c98a42696e95e7dbe","tid":227550,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"尋日坐九巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐正雙層巴士舊款兩排對坐<br />\n對面坐咗一家三口老夫少妻3歲細路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6bYBkj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6bYBkj.jpg&h=da8550ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個女人係咁用譚式廣東話大聲講電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔理個細路女個個站都玩落車鐘<br />\n最後個巴士司機發現到都自行飛站算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然而個六/七十幾歲呀大叔擘大隻腳係咁挖鼻屎<br />\n之後將隻手放喺雙腳中間想啲鼻屎掃落張凳度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我睇到緊係怒bear佢啦<br />\n然後佢竟然放棄痴鼻屎落張凳度<br />\n改為摸個女塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個女仔兩邊皮膚都好滑<br />\n唯獨有個位係紅咗生幾粒瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁啱又係呀大叔隻手摸個位<br />\n明哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲人一家三口20年前都完全唔存在喺香港架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲珍禽異獸點撚樣落黎香港架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家仲有見過咩腥港蝗族奇事可以分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n交流下有咩大家位要小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d34142d2f7553b5c51e723a431305c52bafe65","tid":227550,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:33:57.000Z","msg":"那有女？"},{"pid":"d6187e3b7eaa802409d7535725ea0c60b6e53ca1","tid":227550,"uid":8264